                        <item xml:id="e1">- Unfilled spaces are left for rubricated passages at the end of the Ms.  &#xD;
- Additional or omitted passages are written in small script in the margins: e.g., fols. 7r, 9v, 12v, 13v, 61v, 71v, 83v, 123r.&#xD;
- Erasures: e.g., fols. 65va, 81rb, 117rb.&#xD;
- Names of the days of the week are written in recent hand: fols. 9v-12r.&#xD;
- Scribbling: fol. 1va, 67r, 130vb, 131r, &#xD;
- Crude drawings: fols. 8v, 9r, 10r, 36r, 130v.</item>
